{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"pain-1","type":"text","text":"### Emotional Stress of Chasing\nFreelancers feel deep anxiety demanding money — fear of sounding rude, damaging relationships, or losing future work. They procrastinate instead of following up.","x":-250,"y":-150,"width":260,"height":110,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"pain-2","type":"text","text":"### Cash Flow Starvation\nCorporate Net-30/60 terms treat freelancers like unsecured creditors. Unpredictable timing makes it impossible to plan rent, taxes, or expenses.","x":-250,"y":0,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"pain-3","type":"text","text":"### Forgotten Invoices\nScattered tools (spreadsheets, sticky notes, calendar alerts) cause admin fatigue. Freelancers forget to track or even send invoices — losing thousands.","x":-250,"y":140,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"pain-4","type":"text","text":"### Decision Fatigue\n\"What tone should I use? Is it too soon to follow up? Am I being too aggressive?\" — No script, no system, just guesswork every time.","x":-250,"y":280,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"pain-5","type":"text","text":"### Manual Admin Waste\nHours spent on spreadsheet archaeology — copying email templates, manually matching deposits, context-switching between tools instead of doing billable work.","x":-250,"y":420,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"solution-header","type":"text","text":"## How ChaseFree Solves It","x":820,"y":-230,"width":220,"height":45,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sol-1","type":"text","text":"### AI Tone-Calibrated Reminders\n4 presets: Friendly Nudge → Professional → Firm → Final Notice. AI drafts perfectly-toned emails based on days overdue. No blank-page anxiety.","x":820,"y":-150,"width":260,"height":110,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sol-2","type":"text","text":"### \"Who to Chase Today\" Dashboard\nAlgorithm-prioritized list of unpaid invoices. Shows exactly who needs attention today — overdue days, amount, client name. One-click \"Generate Reminder\" button.","x":820,"y":0,"width":260,"height":110,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sol-3","type":"text","text":"### Unbilled Scratchpad\nQuick-dump sticky notes for completed work. Never forget to invoice again. Convert tasks to invoices with one click. Automated weekly cron reminders.","x":820,"y":150,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sol-4","type":"text","text":"### Context-Aware AI Generator\nAI uses invoice details, client history, reminder count, and overdue duration to generate 2-3 natural-sounding variants. User picks the one that \"sounds like them.\"","x":820,"y":290,"width":260,"height":110,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sol-5","type":"text","text":"### Smart Invoice Builder\nTwo-pane layout: form + live PDF preview. Auto-incrementing invoice numbers, Net-30/60 dropdowns, multiple line items, currency support. Create in seconds, not minutes.","x":820,"y":440,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"j-1","type":"text","text":"**1. Sign Up**\nQuick email registration → 5-step onboarding survey (name, profession, pain points)","x":250,"y":780,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"j-2","type":"text","text":"**2. Add First Client**\nSimple form or inline creation from invoice page. No friction.","x":250,"y":900,"width":220,"height":60,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"j-3","type":"text","text":"**3. Create First Invoice**\nSmart Builder with live PDF preview. Auto invoice numbers, Net-30 dropdown, line items.","x":250,"y":1000,"width":220,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"j-4","type":"text","text":"**4. See Dashboard**\n\"Who to Chase Today\" panel lights up. Color-coded urgency: red = overdue, yellow = due soon.","x":250,"y":1110,"width":220,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"j-5","type":"text","text":"**5. Generate Reminder**\nSelect tone → AI drafts 3 options → Copy to clipboard → Send via Gmail. Mark as sent.","x":250,"y":1220,"width":220,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tech-stack","type":"text","text":"**Built with:** Next.js 16 · React 19 · Tailwind 4 · Supabase · AI (OpenAI-compatible)\n\n**Security:** Row-Level Security · Rate Limiting · XSS Prevention · CSP Headers","x":820,"y":-460,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"value-header","type":"text","text":"## Value Proposition","x":280,"y":-780,"width":200,"height":105,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"pain-header","type":"text","text":"## The Problem","x":-200,"y":-280,"width":200,"height":45,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"stat-2","type":"text","text":"**Key Metric:** Time from sign-up to first AI reminder draft = under 5 minutes","x":-200,"y":-430,"width":280,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"stat-1","type":"text","text":"**Target:** Solo freelancers, independent contractors, micro-agencies (designers, developers, writers, consultants)","x":-200,"y":-550,"width":280,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"journey-header","type":"text","text":"## The User Journey","x":270,"y":680,"width":200,"height":45,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"value-3","type":"text","text":"### The Differentiator\nChaseFree is NOT accounting software. It's an emotional painkiller — a focused workflow tool that turns the awkward collections process into a calm, 2-minute daily routine.","x":315,"y":-990,"width":320,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"value-1","type":"text","text":"### For Freelancers\n\"Stop agonizing over unpaid invoices. Our AI tracks what you're owed and writes the perfect follow-up email — so you never guess what to say.\"","x":80,"y":-1210,"width":250,"height":90,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"value-2","type":"text","text":"### For Small Agencies\n\"Professional invoicing with Net-30 terms, PDF generation, and tone-escalation that protects client relationships while getting you paid.\"","x":510,"y":-1255,"width":250,"height":90,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# ChaseFree AI\n## The Founder's Pitch\n\n*AI-powered invoicing & payment follow-up assistant for freelancers and small agencies*","x":200,"y":-550,"width":360,"height":120,"color":"6"}
	],
